nodes.text: Darin De Paul provided the voice of Tenebrae and General Daeruun amongst others in Star Wars: The Old Republic, the Weequay in Star Wars Battlefront: Outer Rim and Varond Jelik and "old" Anakin Skywalker in LEGO Star Wars: The Force Awakens.
